Package: documentoR
Type: Package
Title: AI-powered Project Documentation for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Lazaro", family = "Alvarez", email = "you@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scan an R project, summarize files using an LLM (via ellmer or a user-supplied chat function), and generate per-file markdown, an index.json, and a README.md. Designed for safe, repeatable documentation runs and easy CI integration.
